Package: cstemplate
Title: Shared pkgdown House Style for the cs* Package Family
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person(c("Richard","Aubrey"), "White", email = "hello@rwhite.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6747-1726"))
  )
Description: A pkgdown template package that gives every cs* package a
    consistent Bootstrap 5 house style: Spectral + Source Sans 3 typography,
    the navy/coral palette, a shared navbar with a "cs* family" switcher,
    and a common footer. Packages opt in with
    template: { package: cstemplate } in their own _pkgdown.yml.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://niphr.github.io/cstemplate/, https://github.com/niphr/cstemplate
BugReports: https://github.com/niphr/cstemplate/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Config/Needs/website: pkgdown
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
